room_title: Escape room "Curse of Anubis" by Escape On 13th in Salt Lake City
room_address: 342 W 1300 S Salt Lake City, UT 84101
room_description: You are an archaeologist exploring the dark passages of a forgotten temple when suddenly a stone door closes behind you. You look around to find that you are not alone, that the skeletons of other lost adventurers are all around you. Can you uncover the mystery of this lost temple? Time is running out. Escape the Curse of Anubis before this tomb becomes your own.
